             was indicted for <rs id="t17801206-18-off93" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17801206-18-off93" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17801206-18-off93" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a cloth great coat, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17801206-18-victim199" type="victimName">
                     Nicholas 
                     Delevitt
                  <interp inst="t17801206-18-victim199" type="surname" value="Delevitt"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17801206-18-victim199" type="given" value="Nicholas"></interp>
